attributionInfo.brokerName: Keller Williams Realty Boston-Metro | Back Bay

description: Exceptional 2 bedroom, 2 bath condominium situated in a highly sought after South Boston neighborhood. This well-appointed building is centrally located overlooking M St Park and is within walking distance of the Seaport, East Broadway, Castle Island and is on the very desirable East First St corridor. The interior finishes in this dramatic condominium will exceed your every expectation: Stylish Chef’s kitchen with a professional grade appliance package including direct venting hoods, custom cabinets, granite counter tops, spa like baths, hardwood floors, great ceiling height, large windows, excellent natural light and a private deck. This building has been professionally designed and offers tastefully finished common areas, private storage and parking. This property is truly in one of South Boston's finest locations and with new neighboring developments the potential is endless.
